# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Stable)

## Summary
The piano is stable and prevents accidental repeat notes.

## Fixes
- **No More Machine Gun**: Prevents a single motion from playing the same note multiple times.
- **Reset Logic**: You must "stop" (velocity drops) before you can strike again.
- **Precision**: High velocity threshold (0.15) ensures only deliberate hits.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
